<p> Rock Paper Scissors is a game where two players simultaneously choose one of three
shapes (rock, paper or scissors) usually by indicating with their hands.
This game has one of two outcomes: a draw, or a win for one player and a loss for the other.</p>

<p>This game is usually played using the players hands; a closed fist represents
a rock, two fingers extended (similar to the Peace Symbol) represents scissors
and a flat hand represents paper.</p>
<br></br>

<p>The Player wins using one of the following conditions:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Rock breaks Scissors</li>
  <li>Scissors cut Paper</li>
  <li>Paper covers Rock</li>
</ol>
